skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: noise of waterfall
des: Fall into a deep sleep with our dreamy and waterfall sounds. Noise of Waterfall is the ultimate science-backed companion for relaxation, focus, and better sleep. \n\nAll you need to do is say Alexa start Noise of Waterfall, and she will play the track for 30 minutes. This is a perfect skill to leave on while you are asleep, to use for relaxation and meditation, or to tune in and focus on your work.
